46:26.910 --> 46:28.696
Yes.

46:28.787 --> 46:30.527
Oh, yes.

46:30.622 --> 46:31.611
Look at them.

46:32.499 --> 46:34.785
They're laughing about this.

46:35.251 --> 46:37.833
