47:59.294 --> 48:00.704
-Right.
-I gave him the Seals casings.

48:00.795 --> 48:03.207
He signed for them.

48:03.298 --> 48:05.289
He's in on this cover-up.

48:05.383 --> 48:07.374
(SIGHS)

48:08.803 --> 48:10.839
This reporter, or whatever he is, blogger,

48:10.930 --> 48:14.058
