49:03.191 --> 49:04.180
What?

49:13.910 --> 49:14.990
(HAMMERING)

49:23.545 --> 49:25.206
Yeah, right here.

49:34.389 --> 49:35.424
Can I help you with something?

49:36.141 --> 49:37.881
