49:39.477 --> 49:41.308
Hold on, hold on. Slow down, now.

49:41.396 --> 49:42.431
Don't tell me slow down.

49:42.522 --> 49:45.138
Y'all the ones in a hurry
to bulldoze the goddamn city.

49:45.233 --> 49:48.475
