and it was bleeding all over the place.

50:12.260 --> 50:14.672
-Don't give me that look.
-Alcide.

50:14.762 --> 50:16.013
There are glasses on the counter.

50:16.097 --> 50:18.839
Would you please fill them with water?

50:18.933 --> 50:20.389
