Boys, go to your room, please.

50:45.543 --> 50:47.124
-What's wrong?
-Just go.

50:47.212 --> 50:48.201
(PHONE BEEPS)

50:55.303 --> 50:56.292
(BEEP)

50:56.387 --> 50:58.799
